* Create\nMaterialized Views
** Precompute & cache query results
***_ Stored as Delta table
***_ Faster than standard views
** CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW statement
***_ Optional SCHEDULE for auto-refresh
** Refresh strategies
***_ Incremental: only changed data
***_ Full: reprocess everything
** Incremental requires
***_ Delta source tables
***_ Row tracking enabled
** Best for
***_ Complex aggregations
***_ Frequently queried data
***_ Dashboard performance
@endmindmap
